title: Microsoft Office 2013 SP1 X86 Pro Plus VL MULTi-12 {Generation2}
description:
* Microsoft Office 2013 SP1 X86 Professional Plus VL MULTi-12 {Generation2}


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and eleven exe-files.

* All exe-files are created from original MSDN ISO's for each language.

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the 
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source) 
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

* Sources & Hashes attached in a separate .txt 

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language.exe

* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO
 
* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract & recreate the original ISO, fully updated and
* in the selected language.

[ LANGUAGES ] 

* da-DK [ Danish ]
* de-DE [ German ]
* en-US [ English]
* es-ES [ Spanish]
* fi-FI [ Finnish]
* fr-FR [ French ]
* it-IT [ Italian]
* nb-NO [ Norwegian]
* nl-NL [ Dutch ]
* pt-BR [ Brazilian]
* pt-PT [ Portuguese]
* sv-SE [ Swedish ]

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* Office15.X86.en-US.iso Size: 2,15GB

* To activate Office, use Microsoft Toolkit.
* Extract attached MTKV253.zip, click the Office button,
* install AutoKMS, and then click the Activate button.
